</title>
<subSubSection id="EFCD66305366B2F389E2E4F870E9D46F" pageId="null" pageNumber="439" type="description">
<paragraph id="8A987C81B3A996E6FEEBFAED11DECAF8" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">
Habitus, 
<normalizedToken id="4226108628FE4C9F6D44C2A986D68BD0" originalValue="Ausläufer" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Auslaeufer</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="3A2C20BA5F62377D209160DF65E8B467" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
, Stengel und 
<normalizedToken id="A4E6F7AD580FBD0AE152F733CA3C442B" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="982C6133DA12FCB46EA3DC44186C47A1" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Carex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="439" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="praecox">
<emphasis id="C823C5D0942C880696A93286DC864E40" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">C. praecox</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr.27). 
<normalizedToken id="FD5D7D07D0F981DDF81556A47840C68A" originalValue="Tragblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Tragblaetter</normalizedToken>
wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="2F9A5975038C27407E9F3472D1457C40" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Carex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="439" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="praecox">
<emphasis id="69982BCE4012A8D45B75AFB290B25CC3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">C. praecox</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, jedoch 
<normalizedToken id="FD9BBC21E91C681F91F4F425CE1255EF" originalValue="kürzer" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">kuerzer</normalizedToken>
, meist ⅔ 
<emphasis id="1D8D8313779920023021AEBA31819C0A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">
so lang wie die reifen 
<normalizedToken id="9CF13ED748B63C28F1C5E7CBB1CBE390" originalValue="Fruchtschläuche" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Fruchtschlaeuche</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="7E055A27CA20A75B5C2574BA149C23EF" originalValue="Fruchtschläuche" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Fruchtschlaeuche</normalizedToken>
3,5
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="EEBEFD80325BA4E157A3BD5F40224892" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">4,5 mm lang</emphasis>
, im untern Drittel am breitesten (
<emphasis id="85968D5B3038DD6CEBD9E01C3EBACDBC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">1-1,5 mm</emphasis>
), Querschnitt, Nervatur und 
<normalizedToken id="E1434A37A18CA43A09EA158D8E7DA708" originalValue="Oberfläche" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Oberflaeche</normalizedToken>
wie bei 
<emphasis id="49CCC19D6EB89D6240289313F7CDF5B1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">
<taxonomicName id="94A6C1781DB45A7CC94311C9AF3404D8" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Carex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="439" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="praecox">C. praecox</taxonomicName>
; 
<normalizedToken id="58BF89758C8C3719A8978D9CF83DBA78" originalValue="Flügel" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Fluegel</normalizedToken>
am Rand jedoch erst etwa in der Mitte beginnend, 0,1
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="72A4083188A5BABA6C64C682D8122BBB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">0,2 mm breit;</emphasis>
Fruchtschlauch 
<emphasis id="F4270C72A51D0A36BDF28C27A7FF4BE3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">
<normalizedToken id="DE3B74BCC82A7EC81EF7E277813BBCF9" originalValue="allmählich" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">allmaehlich</normalizedToken>
in den Schnabel 
<normalizedToken id="6EDE91EC644E4D3512B99BDF8C7FA1EE" originalValue="verschmälert" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">verschmaelert</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
Narben 2.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="604A23B837AF43B378C51C36395CF1ED" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">
<emphasis id="31D59034B90B098E0E3B959942593500" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="761F39C80EF6F7BDE20336BB2C34C24B" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">
<emphasis id="2D8421268B6E95CD076770669FEE9078" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Wahrscheinlich wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="66FC53392AEA02E2F9E6AE35986B6929" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Carex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="439" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="praecox">
<emphasis id="BCC6FD1B837516BAF44D9CC7DDC7D875" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">C. praecox</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 27). Wird auch von 
<normalizedToken id="C5966285E57BD2DDF4575DEBB1C381D0" originalValue="Waldrändern" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Waldraendern</normalizedToken>
angegeben.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3E2C5D462D50D07F435DD989E1CE9BE9" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">
<emphasis id="827A7EC0E99CB3AF23EFB04CAC9D354F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">
<pageBreakToken id="E8C6666D083F50D5B34C33460A5B8BF0" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Verbreitung</pageBreakToken>
.
</emphasis>
(
<normalizedToken id="B47562E830451DAE25162A1EEFCD31CE" originalValue="Unvollständig" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Unvollstaendig</normalizedToken>
bekannt, da oft nicht von 
<taxonomicName id="A15EFD0D4D06BB313EB91F801612F164" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Carex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="439" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="praecox">
<emphasis id="7BE59F169393E2185F6261D0A9C364AB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">C. praecox</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
unterschieden.) 
<emphasis id="D52723DD78F6BFF97080E46C059DF9BA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">
Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="A605BC97A4FDDF26D224B3F4460EB05A" originalValue="osteuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">osteuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
Rheingebiet bis 
<normalizedToken id="9EDE45BBEA8807BDB5C2BE5D14333427" originalValue="Siebenbürgen" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Siebenbuergen</normalizedToken>
. - Im Gebiet: Oberrheinische Tiefebene bei Colmar und Wittelsheim, Schwarzwald (Waldrand des Buchholen 
<normalizedToken id="F52BD5E6B39724A7612745DA802F1704" originalValue="nördlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">noerdlich</normalizedToken>
Wollbach bei 
<normalizedToken id="BB680BF21C8D1B6F82A073CE23F0D800" originalValue="Lörrach" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Loerrach</normalizedToken>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="32F5638A2F6BB21F16AC275310BA12F1" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">
<emphasis id="12D4A1F24CF212A75EB049173B0EAD64" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">
Bemerkungen. 
<taxonomicName id="71723EDBD6EA37650F90A48F31D815AE" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Carex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="439" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="curvata">C. curvata</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
ist nahe verwandt mit 
<emphasis id="DAE387639C1590E22E1B84C1EEE4B12A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">
<taxonomicName id="203B1BAA5B6B80CC06AD192B78106703" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Carex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="439" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="praecox">C. praecox</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Die beiden Arten 
<normalizedToken id="97F5519BF1B7DACD4C7CF583D9BFCD10" originalValue="können" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">koennen</normalizedToken>
nur an den reifen 
<normalizedToken id="DA80F9C869C077C9B46BD55BBC6EDC9D" originalValue="Fruchtschläuchen" pageId="null" pageNumber="439">Fruchtschlaeuchen</normalizedToken>
unterschieden werden.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</treatment>
